' 1.13 check_res
' ===========================================================================
' CHECKRES.LST
'
' Use this procedure to find the current screen resolution and store
' this value in a Global byte sized variable named res:
'      0=ST Low, 1=ST Medium, 2=ST High         <-- with all GFA versions
'      7=TT Low, 4=TT Medium, 6=TT High         <-- with GFA 3.6 only
' ===========================================================================
'
PROCEDURE check_res
  res=XBIOS(4)                          ! Global byte variable
RETURN
